org.jasig.cas.authentication

Class SuccessfulHandlerMetaDataPopulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.authentication.SuccessfulHandlerMetaDataPopulator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuthenticationMetaDataPopulator

    @Component(value="successfulHandlerMetaDataPopulator")
public class SuccessfulHandlerMetaDataPopulator
extends java.lang.Object
implements AuthenticationMetaDataPopulator
    Sets an authentication attribute containing the collection of authentication handlers (by name) that successfully authenticated credential. The attribute name is given by SUCCESSFUL_AUTHENTICATION_HANDLERS. This component provides a simple method to inject successful handlers into the CAS ticket validation response to support level of assurance and MFA use cases.
    Since:
    4.0.0
